name: A-Forest
body:
A-Forest is a theme who cares about animation, transparency and artwork.
You can get it from Theme Chooser.

If you want help me in the development or testing feel free to contact me (federico.ferri@yahoo.it).
Your help is very appreciated

For any kind of request feel free to mail me or add a issue.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
